    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Known as Puca is an auto-battle rogue-lite game that requires strategy and planning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect and strengthen the naughty fairy Puca and correct Puca's inclination toward bad spirits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030130/extras/36d28f6467112ca375ba6c34cbc48dd3.poster.avif?t=1755831803\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030130/extras/36d28f6467112ca375ba6c34cbc48dd3.webm?t=1755831803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030130/extras/36d28f6467112ca375ba6c34cbc48dd3.mp4?t=1755831803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Each Puca has different characteristics. Collect Pucas with the same trait to strengthen them efficiently.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　You may encounter special Puca as you complete quests. Each special Puca has powerful unique abilities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　Pucas have a limited amount of time to exist. How much you can accomplish in that time depends on your strategy and planning.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030130/extras/2bf3b3f81abd15e4868c8d6d392c473e.poster.avif?t=1755831803\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030130/extras/2bf3b3f81abd15e4868c8d6d392c473e.webm?t=1755831803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030130/extras/2bf3b3f81abd15e4868c8d6d392c473e.mp4?t=1755831803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030130/extras/3f45931af653a203ef1bc2eee4ec7724.poster.avif?t=1755831803\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030130/extras/3f45931af653a203ef1bc2eee4ec7724.webm?t=1755831803\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030130/extras/3f45931af653a203ef1bc2eee4ec7724.mp4?t=1755831803\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
